r of iterator elements.\r\n\r\nPatches\r\n\r\nThis has been fixed in crossbeam-channel 0.4.4.\r\n\r\n\r\nReferences\r\nSee crossbeam-rs/crossbeam#533, crossbeam-rs/crossbeam#539, and rustsec/advisory-db#425 for more details.", "created_at": "2022-06-07T09:14:10Z", "updated_at": "2022-06-07T10:41:46Z", "closed_at": "2022-06-07T10:41:43Z", "merged_at": "2022-06-07T10:41:43Z", "merge_commit_sha": "8aa6dd2f5ce69dea7a499657f3b85f1cfb1bbf72", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tari-project/broadcast_channel/pulls/4/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tari-project/broadcast_channel/pulls/4/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tari-project/broadcast_channel/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tari-project/broadcast_channel/issues/4/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tari-project/broadcast_channel/statuses/eaa8b1a5dcf0ba287bd63f7a73ac53668eefd608", "head": {"label": "tari-project:update-crossbeam", "ref": "update-crossbeam", "sha": "eaa8b1a5dcf0ba287bd63f7a73ac53668eefd608", "user": {"login": "tari-project", "id": 37560539, "node_id": "MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjM3NTYwNTM5", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/37560539?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/tari-project", "html_url": "https://github.com/tari-project", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tari-project/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tari-project/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tari-project/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tari-project/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tari-project/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tari-project/orgs", "repos_url": "